          <h1 id="project-title">BearHug - An Arcade Cabinet</h1>

      <p>BearHug is a non-traditional arcade cabinet featuring two non-traditional digital games that put your reflex and cognitive skills to the test. In Gummy Bear Tease, players puzzle through brain teasing color matching exercises. In First Person Hugger, players decide through observation whether or not characters want to be hugged. Both games use non-traditional game controllers: any acrylic hexagon dial and two mannequin hands.
      <br><br>
      My role in this project:
      <br>
      Unity3D game development using Javascript, game controller fabrication, circuit fabircation and digital fabrication using a CNC router and a 50W laster cutter, design and UX.</p>



      <p>DEM Tales is an interactive, animated, STEM enriched mobile platform. DEM Tales is a call-to-action project to support and provide an alternative curriculum to underserved NYC students.</p>
